Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.84,0:00:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不行的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.81,0:00:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從沒經歷過像樣的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.64,0:00:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面對這種事總是太遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在看到她的眼淚時  我也意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.34,0:00:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮到底是在與什麼作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她為什麼要我回答那些問題  要我說出那些話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:36.51,fix,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\pos(516,376)}水魔導師的攻擊增強了\N請求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及  她為什麼會哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.53,0:00:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有了新的發現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我打算進行探索
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  你沒帶傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是樟葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟樟葉有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身子都涼冰冰的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗住民的體溫從來都是這麼涼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了些菜粥  多少吃點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試著坐起來一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現實世界裡出現了扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為邪王真眼的力量正在衰退…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燒還沒退啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就繼續老老實實睡著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊  都感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天還想硬撐著出門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒走幾步就癱倒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(660,656)}Vanishment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界要消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡了一晚早就完全恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  病沒好之前不准出門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來你天天到底是想去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經說過了  這一點無可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以漆黑烈焰使的身份問你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是想對你怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是你瞞著我出去  讓我覺得有些不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過很快你就會明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要拋下凸守  變成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DeDeDeDeath…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就會好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我願意  隨時都可以借助邪王真眼之力恢復健康
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要服下從邪王崖暗黑壁之巔采來的黑龍花才能痊癒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別再亂加設定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠得太近會被傳染的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人  等著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凸守一定會為你前去…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也謝謝你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過待太久了當心會被傳染
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了奇美拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快痊癒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作業已經攢了一堆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛從你嘴裡說出了禁句
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:04:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘記作業就會皺眉~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36}注：宿題を忘れると顰蹙だい，諧音冷笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來蘇菲婭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我幾次試圖通過電子音信識別暗號與她取得聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她一直沒有回應
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  到底是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說她最近很忙來著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當她說什麼要挑起戰爭時  我就猜到了這種結果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你很早就看出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一眼就看出來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的眼裡都只有你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是十花姐告訴我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是  你打算怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她那麼喜歡你  總不能放任不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這麼說  我也不知道該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她從來也沒說出口過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼突然又裝正經了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是說實話嘛  我到底該怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情女生應該更懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我怎麼會懂這些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在逃避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒逃避呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就別多管閒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花的事情那時也是這樣  一有點問題就過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是看你們沒辦法了  才想來幫忙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又沒求你來幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  隨你便好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香學姐  我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不幹什麼就別把人絆倒！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她搞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:06:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱旋歸來！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在搞什麼呢  一不小心會出人命的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要戰勝內在的自己  需要波紋和魔法能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別信她的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來  我就已經克服了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取得了最終勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後的我就是魔法魔王少女·改+α外傳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽起來就像是不斷砸牌子的續作遊戲一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  之前的事已經被永遠留在遺忘的盡頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,統統消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮  這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是天使的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富樫君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會把她剛才的話當真了  以為一切都沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她那只是在逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然知道  我和七宮認識也不是一兩天了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你要我怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們不是都說「戀愛就像是一場夢」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是一場夢  時間久了自然就會醒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非要把她叫醒的話  只會讓她更痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不關你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小森大人其實最喜歡你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花  小凸  你  還有七宮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她最喜歡你們這些中二病了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都有些羡慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時候都想  要是我也是中二病就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐你？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話  我就能和大家分享同樣的心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是中二病又不是想當就能當的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從你嚮往中二病的一刻起  就已經很中二了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐你不是第二代邪王真眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘇菲婭  我知道你很迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說你已經恢復記憶了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要吃藥草嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為了更好地跟你溝通才專門換上這些行頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裙子已經很緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘇菲婭  我有話要授予你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是魔術師森大人的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我過去曾與冒名之人戰鬥  向其予以了懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.01,0:10:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候我意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該如何面對心中的另一個自己  如何與她戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一個自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  想要瞭解自身  便需要著眼於外界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我通過於冒名之人戰鬥  得以瞭解了自己那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘇菲婭  你也有需要打倒的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找到那個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時  前途就會出現在你眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死我了  你懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森大人  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來給你補充魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太近啦  別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是雷霆戰錘使  快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙  不光要對漆黑烈焰使下手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在連冒牌森大人也不放過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樟葉  月亮出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多漂亮的滿月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來今晚是「藍月」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36}注：「藍月」，每隔2到3年出現一次的額外的滿月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼藍之月…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮喜歡我  但我心裡有六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不懂  太複雜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者  不  漆黑烈焰使
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想看看我的魔法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經過了長久的尋找  我才發現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要打倒的對手  只有你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能這樣來解決
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  開戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:11:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔王認證
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  啊  智音姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  六花姐不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才稍微沒留意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚是藍月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想她大概察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜是蒼藍之月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼藍之月？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗炎龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者你說過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉睡在自己體內的暗炎龍又要覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己也想讓其覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自遠古以來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永恆不變的絕對契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使越過時間  跨過次元
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往平行世界的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這份契約依舊延續
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以此絕對力量而出現在我面前的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾在如今這混沌不堪  並且不屬於自己的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因強力的封印之力以及被篡改的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而被奪走了真正的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾恐怕在不遠的將來就會歸於虛無
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此吾託付於汝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓沉睡於吾體內的暗炎龍  重現於世吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喚醒足以吞噬這個錯誤的世界  並且變革它的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復活暗炎龍的鑰匙有三把
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Skuld
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯庫爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Verdandi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薇兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Urd
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兀兒德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36}注：諾恩三女神，斯庫爾德掌管未來，薇兒丹蒂掌管現在，兀兒德掌管過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是吾之絕對契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有與吾同生共死的力量之人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到這三把鑰匙不在話下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永恆的契約者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾暫時進入睡夢  靜候那個時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,望即將來臨的青色月夜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝能賜予我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是藏身地點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記不大清了  不過應該在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這給…挖成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是邪王真眼留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是記錄這裡已經找過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…那她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也找過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼都找不到的兀兒德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送往過去的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要將鑰匙送往過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能利用平行世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那筆記中提到平行世界的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:14:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在第十四座鐵塔投射的影子中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不知道從哪裡開始數
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她準備挨個的嘗試…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  但是馬上就真相大白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙一直都為此…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  大概知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一塊的景色還稍微有點印象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花  你無論何時都認真地中二著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論何時都認真地戀愛著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直為我著想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花  六花  六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太  這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兀兒德？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都感冒了還跑來找這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒加重了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  你說過需要絕對的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永恆的契約者來喚醒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是勇太永恆的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以必須要找到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到然後證明自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用做這些也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:17:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我明明是契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻一把鑰匙都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而蘇菲婭她…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太你是我的契約者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我是你絕對的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我初二的那個夏天骨折了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把它埋在了當時的石膏裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真能做這麼麻煩的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是這樣誰也不會明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在金屬上刻字非常難  中途放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都已經是好幾年前的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然還留著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就只是個石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是喚醒暗炎龍的魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼藍之月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候我查過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是藍月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花  不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了  邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之永遠契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆裂吧  現實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崩斷吧  神經
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(620,656)}Vanishment  this  world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧  這個世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者  不  GelZone  UNSAS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開戰了  讓我跟暗炎龍一決勝負  傾盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該與之戰鬥的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須要面對的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是與勇者一同思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與勇者一同追尋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與勇者一同放棄的暗炎龍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我必須面對的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要分出勝負的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮…我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃GelZone  UNSAS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將世界毀滅並重建之人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法魔王少女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你渴望永恆的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就用雙眼來見證吾暗炎龍的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗炎龍並不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然也看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何…何方妖孽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後六花感冒又犯  躺在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太  讓時光回轉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到7月8號那天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊被毀滅性的作業壓迫著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊迎來了暑假的結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:20:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作業做不完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢葉長大了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢葉也要聽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果我一次也沒去過雅加達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的作業沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於新生蘇菲婭來講小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮在跟暗炎龍的戰鬥之後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進化成了新的七宮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.60,0:21:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底哪裡變了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會改變  永遠都是魔法魔王少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我以不變之名義  破壞積累之物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不再改變而需求著變得更為強大的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是難不成這就是連關天則嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  這就是連關天則
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也要去找天使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我說啊  勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
